342285.「ただいまより 第１４回\n アストルティア・クイーン コンテストに\n 参加す:
It's time to introduce the fierce beauties
who will be participating in this year's
14th Annual Astoltia Queen Contest!

342286.「前大会で 好成績をおさめ\n 見事 出場権を獲得した ３名に加え……:
And now, joining the 3 winners with excellent
results from last year's contest...

342287.「総勢４８人の ライバル同士による\n 熾烈な予選を勝ち抜いた 上位５名！\n:
From a total of 48 contestants, we have five
lucky ladies who survived the preliminaries!
8 beauties will aim for the top!

342288.「まずは 前大会の覇者が 堂々の登場だ！\n 出場するたびに じわじわと 順位を:
First upーour reigning champion makes her magnificent entrance! With each competition she's climbed the ranks, finally reaching the
top! A truly elegant lady she is!

342289.「偉大なる母こそが 至高のクイーン！\n 夫のパドレもナイトを制し 最強夫婦を阻:
The magnificent mother is also supreme queen! Her husband Padre was also crowned Knightー can anyone hope to stop this power couple?!
It's the Elegant from Ages PastーMarone!

342290.「昨年は 夫のパドレと 夫婦そろって\n クイーンとナイトになれて うれしかった:
It was truly an honor that Padre and I were
both crowned Knight and Queen last year.
Thank you all so much for your support.

342291.「今日は ふたりで 皆さんにお礼をいいたくて\n パドレにも 来てもらったのよ。:
I asked Padre to join us here today so that
we could both thank you all.
Isn't that right, dear?

342292.「こんな幸せを また今年も……なんて ちょっと\n 欲張りね。今回は 順位を忘れ:
It may seem greedy of me to hope for the same happiness as last year. Instead, I'm just going to enjoy myself without worrying about
how well I do. Please come and chat with me if you'd like.

342293.「続きまして 惜しくも 首位を明け渡した\n 先代クイーンの このお方！:
Next up...our previous queen who unfortunately
lost her top spot!

342294.「光輪をいただく その姿は まさに天衣無縫！\n 空をはばたく その姿は 神々を:
Adorned with a halo, her appearance is truly without flaw! Her soaring through the skies can captivate even the gods! The Eternal
Archangel, Lectalis!

342295.「また きみたちに会えて うれしいよ。\n こうやって 話したり 触れあったりで:
I'm so glad to see everyone again. Being
able to talk like this, to connect with you
all... It means so very much to me.

342296.「さあ ぼくの手を取って。\n また一緒に クイーンの座を求め 旅をしよう。\n:
So take my hand...we'll soar together to
search for the Queen's throne once more.
Please...keep watch over me.

342297.「続いては 前回 前々回と ３位に輝き\n その威厳を示した 魔界の女王の登場だ:
Shining in third place both last year and the
year before, our next contestant is none other
than the queen of the Demon World!

342298.「輝く……だと？\n 二度も ３位に甘んじるとは\n 我が威光も ずいぶんと 落:
Shining...? To be content with third place
not once, but twice...
There's nothing "shining" about that...

342299.「ひいっ！ その絶対零度の眼光こそ 最恐の証！\n 武勇ひとつで 戦乱の世を の:
Eeek! That absolute-zero stare is the surefire proof of her terror! Rising above a war-torn world through sheer bravery...it's the
Reigning Ice Witch, Valeria!

342300.「これまで どんな難局であろうと\n 我が大矛で なぎ払ってきた……。:
Until now, nothing could match the might
of my great spear...

342301.「今年こそ クイーンの座を取りもどし\n 魔界の民への 手土産とさせてもらおう。:
I will reclaim the throne as Queen, offering
it as gratitude to my people. Those who
stand in my way will know death!

342302.「ここからは 激しい予選を 勝ち抜いた５名を\n ご紹介！ 予選第１位を 勝ち取:
We will now introduce the five contestants who
made it through the preliminaries! Placing
first is this familiar and most gentle girl!

342303.「初登場から 毎年欠かさず 皆勤賞だ！\n いてくれるだけで ベホマ級の安心感！:
She's not missed a single year, folks! Just having her here feels like a Fullheal! You know her, you love herーthe Blue Guide
of Al-Ahagiro, Seraphi!

342304.「やっほー！ みんな～！ 会いたかったよ！\n さっそく いつものアレ やろうと:
Hello, everyone! I really missed you all!
I'm thinking of doing my usual, but...which
one should I use this year?!

342305.「ホイミだと思うー？ \n それとも ベホイミかなー？: Maybe a Heal? Or what about a Midheal...?

342306.「それじゃ いっくねーー！\n 正解は～～:
Okay, here I go!
The correct answer this time is...

342307.「とびっきりの～～～ ホイミっ！！\n えへへっ みんな 当たったかな～？:
A super, duper... Heal!!
Hee hee...did you all get it right?

342308.「続いては 予選を第２位で突破！\n どれほど強大な敵だとしても 臆することなく:
Next up is our runner up in the preliminaries!
A great Hero who faces any foe without fear,
protecting the peace!

342309.「強く 正しく 美しく！\n 傷ついても 凛と立ちあがる姿は 勇気の象徴！\n:
Strong, righteous, and beautiful to boot! Even when she's down, she'll always stand back up full of courage! The Battle Princess of
Purity, Anlucia!

342310.「信じてくれる人々が いる限り……\n 私は決して 倒れることは……くっ……。:
As long as there are those who believe in me,
then I will never falter... Ggh...

342311.「やっぱり……まだ 失ったチカラは\n 戻らないの……？:
So...the power I lost still has yet to
return...?

342312.「……代々の勇者と 盟友たちよ。 \n どうか 私にチカラを。:
O Heroes and Allies of old...
Please! Lend me your strength!

342313.「厳しい戦いになることは わかっているの。\n それでも あなたたちとなら なん:
I know this battle won't be easy...but with
all of you, anything is possible! The title
of Queen will be mine once again!

342314.「続きまして 最後の出場は ２０１７年！\n ９年ぶりの再登場にもかかわらず 予:
Our next contestant was last seen back in
2017! Despite a nine-year hiatus, she pulled
off a miracle making it to third place!

342315.「飛び出るアホ毛は お宝レーダー！？\n 財宝求めて 短剣片手に どこまでも！\:
That stray strand of hair...can it really find treasure?! With dagger in hand, she'll go anywhere there's treasure! The Returning
Treasure Hunter, Lynn!

342316.「やばっ！ 久しぶりすぎて\n 段取りを 忘れちゃった！:
Oh, man! It's been so long that I totally
forgot what I'm supposed to do!

342317.「短剣の導きで 再びここに 戻ってこられたわ！\n だって 私にはわかるの。\n:
My dagger showed me the way back here!
This castle's full of treasures just waiting
to be found! I just know it!

342318.「クイーンになったら あの人も\n 見つけてくれるかしら……なんてね。:
If I become Queen, then maybe he'll find
me... Who knows?

342319.「めくるめく秘宝も クイーンの座も\n まとめて このあたしが いただきよっ<h:
I'll take both treasure AND throne all for
myself!

342320.「続いて 予選４位で突破した\n 今 もっともアツい こちらの方に\n ご登場い:
Next up, placing in fourthーlet's welcome
our hottest contender to the stage!

342321.「ちいさな身体に でっかい食い意地！\n グルメを求め アストルティア全土を練り:
She's small, but her huge appetite takes her
all over in search of the finest food! It's
the Bright Blooming Flower, Porte!

342322.「このお城って ほんと 甘くっていい匂～い！\n どこもかしこも おいしそうなお:
This castle smells soooo good! There's so many
delicious looking sweets here...I can't choose
just one!

342323.「あたしがクイーンになったら お茶会しようよ！\n そしたら ここのお菓子 食べ:
If I become Queen, we'll all have a tea party!
All you can eat sweets, too! That's why you
should vote for me!

342324.「さあ！ いよいよ ラスト１名は\n 予選５位に食いこんで ４年ぶりのカムバック:
Last, but not least! A kind-hearted artist
who made fifth place, making a comeback
after a four-year absence!

342325.「女神のような 慈愛に満ちた ほほえみは\n 魔瘴の大地をも 明るく照らす！\n:
Her divine demeanor and compassionate smile
illuminate even the lands of miasma! The
Merciful Maiden of Light, Illusia!

342326.「また ここに来れたら いいなって\n ずっと 夢見てたから……うれしい。:
I dreamed that I'd be able to come back here
again... I'm so glad.

342327.「もう一度 クイーンになれますようにって\n 絵を描いたの。この願いを かなえら:
I drew something, hoping that I'd become Queen again... For this wish of mine to come true, I ask that those in the Demon World would lend
me even just a little of your strength.

342328.「……以上 ８名の美女たちが\n クイーンの座をかけて コンテストを争います。:
And so...these 8 beauties will compete to see
who is most deserving to be called Queen.

342329.「栄光の座に かがやくのは\n 果たして 誰なのか！？\n それを決めるのは あ:
Who will rise to the top this time?! It's up
to you to decide!

342330.「どうですか <pc>さん。\n 今回も選りすぐりの美女が そろいました。\n:
Well, what do you think? There's an amazing
selection of beautiful women for you to choose
this time. Who's your favorite?

342331.「クイーンにふさわしいと思う 美女が決まったら\n あなたの持つ票を 投じてあげ:
If you think any of these beauties deserves
to be Queen, then cast your votes!

342332.「なお 投票につきましては 集計係モカの所で\n おこなっていただくことに なっ: Please go and see Mocha if you'd like to vote.

342333.「票を投じましたら お話がありますので\n 私の所に お立ち寄りください。\n:
After voting, come back and see me so we
can chat. I'll be waiting outside!

342334.「ただいまより 第１４回\n アストルティア・クイーン コンテストの\n 結果発:
We will now announce the results of the 14th
Astoltia Queen Contest!

342335.「この ショコラフォンテヌ城の\n クイーンの座は いったい 誰の手に！？\n:
Who is worthy of being crowned Queen of our
Chocolat Fontenay Castle?! The results are
in!!

342336.「皆さま！ ステージに ご注目ください！:
Ladies and gentlemen! Please look to the
stage!
